In this video I explored some Realistic Survival Games. I looked at several realistic survival games and I tried to see why people would play any of them and if they are worth trying for the first time. These games, DayZ, Stalker GAMMA and Project Zomboid push the limits of realism with immersive gameplay, stunning graphics, and in-depth mechanics. So let’s explore what makes them stand out in the world of Unreal Engine games and find out if they're truly as realistic as they seem.
